Sidaa darteed natiijooyinka ugu daran ee sawirada laabta waxaa badanaa lagu gartaa qaabka ugu daran ee cudurka.
18-kii Febraayo, 2020, baaritaanka cudurka COVID-19 ee ugu horeeyay wuxuu muujiyay qashin-qubka, sameynta xuubka hyaline, soo-galka unugyada loo yaqaan 'interstitial lymphocytes' iyo unugyada syncytial ee sanbabada bukaanka u dhintay cudurka, oo la jaanqaaday cudurka fayraska iyo cudurka 'SDRA', isla markaana la mid ah cudurka bukaannada qaba SARS iyo MERS.
Baaritaanka SARS-CoV-2 RNA ee falcelinta silsiladda polymerase  reverse transcriptase (RT-PCR) ayaa loo isticmaalay sida shuruudaha ugu muhiimsan ee lagu ogaanayo COVID-19.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, sababtoo ah heerka sare ee diidmada been abuurka ah, taas oo dardar gelin karta faafitaanka, muujinta caafimaad ayaa loo adeegsaday baaritaanka (oo aan hadda ka soo bixin oo keliya RT-PCR) Shiinaha Febraayo 13, 2020.
Xaalad la mid ah ayaa dhacday markii la helay cudurka SARS.
Sidaa darteed, isku darka taariikhda cudurka, muuqaalada bukaan socodka, baaritaanka shaybaarka iyo natiijooyinka radiologiga ayaa muhiim ah oo lagama maarmaan u ah helitaanka cudur caafimaad oo wax ku ool ah.
Febraayo 14, 2020, kooxda Feng Zhang waxay sharaxeen hab-maamuus loo adeegsado farsamada CRISPR-ku-saleysan ee SHERLOCK si loo ogaado SARS-CoV-2, taas oo ogaata SARS-CoV-2 RNA-da synthetic ee 20 x 10-18 mol/L ilaa 200 x 10-18 mol/L (10 ilaa 100 nuqul halkii microliter ee soo galaya) iyadoo la adeegsanayo ul cabbirka wax ka yar hal saac, iyada oo aan loo baahnayn qalab adag.
Waxaan rajeyneynaa in farsamada cusub ay si wayn u kordhin karto dareenka iyo faa'iidada marka lagu eego tijaabooyinka kiliinikada.
Sababtoo ah khibrad la'aanta CoV-ga cusub, dhakhaatiirtu waxay awoodaan inay si fiican u siiyaan daaweynta xannibaadda bukaanada COVID-19, isla markaana ay isku dayaan daaweyn kala duwan oo horay loo isticmaalay ama loo soo jeediyay daaweynta CoVs kale sida SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV iyo cudurrada kale ee fayraska (Shaxda (Shaxda2).2).
Daawadahan waxaa ka mid ah daaweyntii hada jirtay iyo tii laga yaabo in la helo daawooyinka ka hortaga fayraska, daawooyinka difaaca jirka, steroids, plasma bukaanada la bogsiiyay, daawooyinka Shiinaha iyo taageero nafsaani ah.
Xitaa plasma laga helo bukaanada soo kabsaday ayaa la soo jeediyay in lagu daaweeyo.
Shirkadaha dawooyinka ayaa ku dadaalaya inay sameeyaan unugyada ka hortaga cudurka iyo tallaalada ka hortaga cudurka.
SARS-CoV-2 wuxuu inta badan weeraraa sambabada marka hore waxaana laga yaabaa inuu sidoo kale weeraro, heer yar, xubnaha kale ee leh ECA2 sida nidaamka mindhicirka iyo kelyaha.
Laakin cillad la'aanta neefsashada iyo burburka xubnaha jidhka ayaa ah khataraha ugu waaweyn ee bukaanka soo wajaha iyo sababaha ugu waaweyn ee dhimashada.
Sidaa darteedna, gargaarka neefsashada waa mid muhiim u ah yareynta calaamadaha iyo badbaadinta nolosha, waxaana ka mid ah daaweynta guud ee oksijiinta, oksijiinta qulqulka sare, hawo-qaadista aan ku dhufatin iyo hawo-qaadista farsamada ee ku dhufatay, iyadoo ku xiran sida ay u daran tahay cudurka.
Bukaannada qaba xanuunka neefsashada ee daran waxay u baahan yihiin in la siiyo oksijiinta dheecaanka jirka (ECMO), oo ah farsamo bedel ah oo loogu talagalay wadnaha iyo sambabada oo loo isticmaalo daaweynta wadnaha ama neefsashada oo daran.
Intaa waxaa dheer, ilaalinta dheelitirka dheelitirka, ka hortagga iyo daaweynta caabuqyada labaad iyo nabarka iyo ilaalinta howlaha xubnaha muhiimka ah ayaa sidoo kale muhiim u ah bukaannada qaba SARS-CoV-2.
Cytosin cascade waxaa la og yahay inay ka dhalanayso falcelinta difaaca jirka ee ka dhacda dadka qaba SARS iyo MERS.
Cytokin cascade waa qaab ka mid ah jawaabta caabuqa ee nidaamka, taas oo lagu garto sii deynta tiro ka mid ah cytokines, oo ay ka mid yihiin TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, iyo MCP-1.
Cytokines-kaani waxay unugyada difaaca jidhka ku dhiirrigeliyaan inay sii daayaan tiro badan oo ah xagjiryo bilaash ah, kuwaas oo ah sababta ugu weyn ee keenta RAS iyo burburka xubnaha badan.
Ka hortagga difaaca jirka ayaa muhiim u ah daaweynta cudurka cytokine cascade, gaar ahaan bukaannada daran.
Kortikosteroids iyo tocilizumab, oo ah anti-IL6 monoclonal antibody ayaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu daaweeyo cytokine cascade.
Daaweynta kale ee ka hortagga difaaca ee Cytokine Cascade waxaa ka mid ah: isbedelka jawaabta difaaca ee T-silooyinka; xannibaadda IFN-y, IL-1, iyo TNF; JAK-ka, blinatumomab; 4 cytokine signaling suppressor; iyo HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids-ka sida immunosuppressants-ka ayaa si weyn loogu isticmaalay daaweynta SARS si loo yareeyo xanuunka caabuqa.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, steroids-ka qaadashada xaddiga sare leh ma aysan faa'iido u lahayn dhaawaca sanbabada ee daran ee ku dhaca SARS iyo COVID-19.
