Enzyme-ka nooca 2 ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin converting enzyme' (ECA2) waa enzyme-ka ku xidhan dusha sare ee unugyada wadnaha, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo mindhicirka.
ECA2 waxay ka hortagtaa waxqabadka angiotensin-ka la xiriira ee loo yaqaan 'angiotensin-converting enzyme' (ECA) iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa qadarka angiotensin II iyo kor u qaadista Ang (1-7), taas oo ka dhigaysa daawo rajo leh oo lagu bartilmaameedsanayo daaweynta cudurada wadnaha.
Nooca bini'aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan 'hECA2'.
Enzyme-ka loo yaqaan 'angiotensin converting enzyme' ee nooca 2 waa metallosymate-ka ku jira zinc-ka oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada 'endothelium' iyo unugyada kale.
ECA2 protein waxaa ku jira N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal domain oo ah amino acid iyo colectrin oo ku jira nidaamka kelyaha.
ECA2 waa protein-ka membrane-ka ee nooca 1 ee hal-mar-mar ah, oo leh domain-ka firfircoon ee loo yaqaan 'enzymatically active domain' oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Qaybta ka baxsan unugyada ECA2 waxaa laga soo saaraa qaybta transmembrane-ka enzyme kale oo la yiraahdo sheddase, waxaana badanaa loo sii daayaa dhiigga kadibna waxaa lagu soo saaraa kaadida.
ECA2 waxay ku jirtaa xubno badan: ECA2 waxay ku xidhan tahay xuubka unugyada unugyada waaweyn ee nooca 2aad ee unugyada wadnaha, unugyada mindhicirka yar, unugyada wadnaha ee wadnaha iyo unugyada wadnaha, iyo unugyada muruqyada ee wadnaha ee unugyada badankood.
Isticmaalka ECA2 mRNA waxaa sidoo kale laga helaa maskaxda, garabka, hypothalamus, iyo maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ECA2 waa inay u shaqeyso sidii ay u adkeyn lahayd ECA.
ECA waxay ka saaraysaa hormoonka angiotensin-ka nooca I ee angiotensin-ka nooca II taasoo keentay xididada xididada.
ECA2 waxay ka soo saarta phenylalanine amino acid carboxyminal ka angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna ku dheecaan angiotensin vasodilator (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 waxay sidoo kale kala gooysaa dhowr peptides oo kale, oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9]-bradicinine, apilin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, iyo ghrelin.
ECA2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa gaadiidka xuubka ee SLC6A19 oo ah amino acid neutral ah waxaana lagu soo daray cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ECA2 waxay u shaqeysaa sida meesha ugu weyn ee laga galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus-yada, oo ay ka mid yihiin HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (viruska sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (viruska sababa COVID-19).
Gaar ahaan, isku xirnaanta borotiinka 'spike protein S1' ee SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 ee domain-ka 'ECA2' ee ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada waxay keentaa 'endocytosis' iyo 'translocation' ee fayraska iyo enzyme-ka ee ku jira endosomes-ka gudaha unugyada.
Geedi socodka soo galitaanka waxaa kaloo u baahan in la diyaariyo borotiinka S ee TMPRSS2 ee martida u ah serine-protease, kaasoo inhibition-kiisa la baaro sida daaweyn la'aan ah. Tani waxay keentay in qaar ka mid ah ay soo jeediyaan in hoos u dhigista heerarka ECA2 ee unugyada laga yaabo inay ka caawiso la dagaalanka caabuqa.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, ururo xirfadlayaal ah iyo hay'ado sharciyeed ayaa ku talinaya in la sii wado caadiga ah ee ka hortagga ECA iyo daaweynta ARB.
